clear day saturday we've got a home game describe 
what that day was for you and the band when did

01:27.477 --> 01:55.172
things begin and so forth The typical Saturday day 
at home would begin for me about 5, 5 30. I'd have to

02:01.450 --> 02:05.217
be up there at 6 30, 6 45 in the morning. At 6 45 when 
you get there, all of them will be there except

02:05.638 --> 02:13.212
maybe a few seniors who haven't gotten up yet. 
