talking getting up at 5 5 30 in the morning and 
getting home at 7 6 37 and it's a it's a full day it's a

03:19.358 --> 03:43.172
full day for them and uh I don't I thought many times 
what in the world makes them do this and I think it's

03:19.358 --> 03:43.172
uh dedication and pride and and uh The love for the 
band and their devotion to each other is the only

03:43.557 --> 03:54.208
things that I have come up with as to why they do 
this. There were no scholarships. There were no

03:55.291 --> 03:56.093
pay. No pay involved. And they do it year after year 
after year. And whatever the demand is on their

04:01.506 --> 04:07.193
time, well, then they do it. And I think those 
