05:37.008 --> 05:49.624
no music majors, we have no, what you would call, 
usually the only playing that most of these guys

05:37.008 --> 05:49.624
get was in the band. So we go up there on the morning 
before the Cotton Bowl performance and we get so

05:50.185 --> 06:02.661
many minutes on the field and the Ohio band goes 
first. and uh we go up in the stands to watch and I

06:03.637 --> 06:29.948
told all the guys in the band to go up and watch them 
